	* message.el (message-remove-duplicates): New function.
	Implementation borrowed from `gnus-remove-duplicates'.
	(message-idna-to-ascii-rhs): Also encode idna addresses in
	Reply-To:, Mail-Reply-To: and Mail-Followup-To:.
